    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Ahro》是一款超凡冒险游戏，故事发生在一个引人入胜、深藏玄机的世界。当你步行或飞翔进行探索时，你会揭示古老但出奇地与现代生活紧密关联的主题。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在游戏中，阿罗可以释放他的灵魂，飞向天空，发现新的物品、地点和秘密。玩家将面临挑战，需要弄清楚如何到达遥不可及的区域并继续前进，同时也会因为好奇心而获得奖励。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 故事始于阿罗开始出现令人不安的精神崩溃症状。在仅从草药中获得轻微缓解后，阿罗就踏上旅程，穿越帝国疆土，去寻找传说中的神奇疗法。随着剧情推进，谜团将愈发深邃，然后逐渐清晰。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▴ <strong>飞翔收集</strong> ▴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817350/extras/a79d5d6345de6d17c3c7770cf8a2c40b.poster.avif?t=1764045976\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817350/extras/a79d5d6345de6d17c3c7770cf8a2c40b.webm?t=1764045976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817350/extras/a79d5d6345de6d17c3c7770cf8a2c40b.mp4?t=1764045976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▴ <strong>探索和发现</strong> ▴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817350/extras/9ae673e4a0578e651dea479223558c80.poster.avif?t=1764045976\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817350/extras/9ae673e4a0578e651dea479223558c80.webm?t=1764045976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817350/extras/9ae673e4a0578e651dea479223558c80.mp4?t=1764045976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▴ <strong>飞翔旅行</strong> ▴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/s